</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upratticus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pratticus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/15/01 7:16:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How do you farm the Spiroc Lord?</span><hr size=1> The trick to the Spiroc Isle is to kill the Vanquishers. If you dont, everything else you kill instantly respawns once its dead.<br>
<br>
There are 3 triads, each lead by a Vanquisher.<br>
<br>
The Lord will continue to immediately respawn at his normal bind spot as long as the Guardian remains alive. As mentioned earlier, make sure you pull him far enough from his spawn point such that when he does die, nothing agros Sirran. Sirran, as far as I know has never died.<br>
<br>
Farm to your hearts content until you have all your Wingblades, then get out of this hellish zone - it makes baby Jesus cry. <p>Pratt Pureblood <BR>
Crusader of Kabald <BR>
Seventh Hammer <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utarnn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tarnn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/15/01 7:06:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How do you farm the Spiroc Lord?</span><hr size=1> the sky diamond is very rare , i recieved one just after the patch, took 13 kills before it dropped I havent heard of it droppin again yet on Tribunal. <br>
<br>
if you really want to get the Girdle you gotta keep at it, take a long time , and alot of lost xp, from death touches, in the 13 lords we killed I died 12 times to DT, and when i helped Shining Path in sky I died on every Lord pull, so if you want the item be prepared to loose some xp, <br>
<br>
I would recomend at least 30 people to do it safely. <br>
<br>
BTW the girdle and the haste spell rock for groupin gwith no chanter, 66 % haste rocks. <br>
<br>
Tarnn 60 Crusader!! <p><img src=http://www.sonic.net/knightstribunal/images/tarnn.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=augie>Augie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/16/01 1:57:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How do you farm the Spiroc Lord?</span><hr size=1> Dealing with Sirran is easy.  Just take another death for the team, that is if you want that belt.  Pull Lord to one spot, kill him, Sirran pops.  Run far away, stun Sirran, run him to a spot far away from the Guardian, original Lord pop spot, and your Lord pull spot.  Then you can pharm Lords at will without a problem. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=13455.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showMessage?topicID=13465.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=13443.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.threadControl?topicID=13443.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13443.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.uns